sequenceDiagram
    actor Gov as Government/Funding Agency
    actor Wholesaler as Seed Wholesaler
    actor Farmer
    actor CCC as Corn Collection Center
    actor CPU as Corn Processing Unit
    actor Dist as Corn Distributor
    actor Retailer as Corn Retailer
    actor User as End User
    participant IPFS
    participant SC as Ethereum Smart Contract Blockchain

    Farmer ->> Gov: 1. Request for fund allocation
    Gov ->> Farmer: 2. Verification & fund allocation
    Gov ->> Wholesaler: 3. Place order for seeds
    Wholesaler ->> Farmer: 4. Supply seeds
    Gov ->> Wholesaler: 5. Release payment
    Farmer ->> IPFS: 6. Send crop growth details

    Farmer ->> CCC: 7. Deliver harvested crop
    CCC ->> CPU: 8. Send crop for processing
    CPU ->> Dist: 9. Process & send corn
    Dist ->> Retailer: 10. Distribute products
    Retailer ->> User: 11. Sell corn products
    User ->> Retailer: 12. Purchase corn products

    note over Gov,SC: All transactions verified on Ethereum Smart Contract
    note over Farmer,IPFS: Crop growth details stored in IPFS
